32:58.268 --> 33:00.978
doesn't mean that I don't do
everything within my power

33:00.979 --> 33:02.480
to help them.

33:06.443 --> 33:08.611
Bob is your soldier.

33:08.612 --> 33:10.446
You made him,

33:10.447 --> 33:12.031
trained him,

33:12.032 --> 33:14.283
and you brought
me in to help him.

33:14.284 --> 33:15.910
That's what I'm gonna do.

33:15.911 --> 33:19.122
So, are you gonna do
this with me or not?

33:22.500 --> 33:24.668
All right,
you guilted me into it.

33:24.669 --> 33:25.794
What's the plan?

33:25.795 --> 33:27.672
We're gonna make
Santa Claus real.

33:29.507 --> 33:31.968
I'm definitely going
to jail for this.

33:33.220 --> 33:34.470
Youyou're back,

33:34.471 --> 33:35.721
