What the hell is that?
Exactly what you think it is.

33:45.315 --> 33:46.982
I was really
counting on my bonus.

33:46.983 --> 33:48.484
Get over to that
switch by the wall.

33:48.485 --> 33:49.652
Jane, don't do this.

33:49.653 --> 33:51.320
lt's treason. lt's Christmas,

33:51.321 --> 33:53.113
