33:53.114 --> 33:56.242
But this won't save me,
they'll just unplug me again.

33:56.243 --> 33:58.619
So what's the point?

33:58.620 --> 34:02.832
Peace on Earth and
good will towards men.

34:12.007 --> 34:14.051
But that's what you are to me,

34:14.052 --> 34:16.012
the pillar in my life.

34:17.681 --> 34:19.139
She loved it.

34:19.139 --> 34:20.724
Of course she did.

34:20.725 --> 34:23.143
Which is nice to see,
but you're still going to jail

34:23.143 --> 34:26.188
and I'm still gonna die,
so, whywhy did we do this?

34:26.188 --> 34:27.563
Come on, Bob.

34:27.565 --> 34:29.525
You're a smart guy.

34:29.525 --> 34:31.985
I'm no longer
an employee of the NSA.

34:31.987 --> 34:34.071
That means no more
mission statement,

34:34.072 --> 34:35.364
no more regulations.

34:35.364 --> 34:37.157
There's nothing holding me back.

34:37.158 --> 34:39.577
Whatwhat does that mean?

34:41.871 --> 34:43.581
He got his wish.

36:37.654 --> 36:39.822
What the hell is
going on in here?

36:39.823 --> 36:41.323
Merry Christmas,
Director Stevens.

36:41.324 --> 36:42.741
All right, that's it.

36:42.742 --> 36:44.827
Shut him down and
detain these two.

36:44.828 --> 36:46.578
I wouldn't do that.

36:46.579 --> 36:48.580
He's got control of the system.

36:48.581 --> 36:50.499
Yeah, I can see that, Chris.

36:50.500 --> 36:52.084
Which part?

36:52.085 --> 36:53.461
All of it.

36:54.963 --> 36:57.715
Okay.

36:57.716 --> 36:59.676
Hold up, everybody.

37:01.761 --> 37:04.471
Bobby, whatcha doin'?

37:04.472 --> 37:07.141
Just spreading some
holiday cheer, Director.

37:07.142 --> 37:08.059
Yeah.

37:08.060 --> 37:10.227
And exactly how much cheer

37:10.228 --> 37:11.187
are we talking?

37:11.188 --> 37:13.188
About $200 billion worth.

37:13.189 --> 37:14.940
 But don't worry.

37:14.941 --> 37:16.358
I fixed the economy.

37:16.359 --> 37:17.651
