37:22.532 --> 37:26.202
The FBI picked up Lucas
T. Wade ten minutes ago.

37:30.206 --> 37:31.665
Great.

37:31.666 --> 37:33.375
So, what happens next?

37:33.376 --> 37:36.337
First, Jane and Chris
face no repercussions.

37:37.839 --> 37:39.923
That's a pretty big ask, Bob.

37:39.924 --> 37:41.216
Well, not to be rude,

37:41.217 --> 37:43.093
