Well...

38:33.978 --> 38:36.605
I just got off the phone
with the President.

38:36.606 --> 38:39.441
That was a fun conversation.

38:39.442 --> 38:41.527
Full pardons for Chris and Jane.

38:41.528 --> 38:42.903
Thank you, Director,

38:42.904 --> 38:46.114
