can have his nukes back now.

38:46.115 --> 38:50.369
God, this is a freaking mess.

38:50.370 --> 38:54.998
You know they're gonna
shut us down for this, Bob.

38:54.999 --> 38:56.542
Shut you down.

38:56.543 --> 38:59.420
It's not much of a dying wish
if I don't die, Director.

39:07.178 --> 39:12.266
So... your wish?

39:12.267 --> 39:13.642
Was it worth it?

39:13.643 --> 39:17.062
Well, for one night,
Santa Claus was real.

39:17.063 --> 39:20.316
I'd say that's pretty
good, wouldn't you?

39:32.662 --> 39:34.955
Is this the same hood?

39:34.956 --> 39:38.334
Do you guys not wash your hoods?

39:41.296 --> 39:44.339
For you.

39:44.340 --> 39:45.300
Hello.

39:45.301 --> 39:46.341
Hello, Jane.

39:46.342 --> 39:47.759
Bob!

39:47.760 --> 39:49.970
They dragged me out of there
before I could say goodbye.

39:49.971 --> 39:51.138
I know.

39:51.139 --> 39:53.473
I told them to, I didn't
want you to be late.

39:53.474 --> 39:55.601
Late for what?

39:55.602 --> 39:57.644
We're here.

39:57.645 --> 40:01.064
Jane Lee, 32, 86 unread emails.

